<SQL>
SELECT "faa" AS "faa", "name" AS "name"
FROM "airports"
WHERE ("faa" = 'GPT')

Collect

library(ggplot2)
mssql_airports %>%
  select(lon, lat) %>%
  filter(lon < 0, lon > -140, lat < 50) %>%
  collect() %>%
  ggplot() +
    geom_point(aes(x = lon, y = lat))

mssql_flights <- tbl(con, "flights")
mssql_flights %>%
  left_join(mssql_airports, by = c("origin" = "name")) %>%
  group_by(origin) %>%
  summarise(flight = n(),
            avg_dep_delay = mean(dep_delay),
            max_dep_delay = max(dep_delay)
            )
NA
show_query({
  mssql_flights %>%
  left_join(mssql_airports, by = c("origin" = "name")) %>%
  group_by(origin) %>%
  summarise(flights =  n(),
            avg_dep_delay = mean(dep_delay),
            max_dep_delay = max(dep_delay))
})
<SQL>
SELECT "origin", COUNT(*) AS "flights", AVG("dep_delay") AS "avg_dep_delay", MAX("dep_delay") AS "max_dep_delay"
FROM (SELECT "TBL_LEFT"."year" AS "year", "TBL_LEFT"."month" AS "month", "TBL_LEFT"."day" AS "day", "TBL_LEFT"."dep_time" AS "dep_time", "TBL_LEFT"."sched_dep_time" AS "sched_dep_time", "TBL_LEFT"."dep_delay" AS "dep_delay", "TBL_LEFT"."arr_time" AS "arr_time", "TBL_LEFT"."sched_arr_time" AS "sched_arr_time", "TBL_LEFT"."arr_delay" AS "arr_delay", "TBL_LEFT"."carrier" AS "carrier", "TBL_LEFT"."flight" AS "flight", "TBL_LEFT"."tailnum" AS "tailnum", "TBL_LEFT"."origin" AS "origin", "TBL_LEFT"."dest" AS "dest", "TBL_LEFT"."air_time" AS "air_time", "TBL_LEFT"."distance" AS "distance", "TBL_LEFT"."hour" AS "hour", "TBL_LEFT"."minute" AS "minute", "TBL_LEFT"."time_hour" AS "time_hour", "TBL_RIGHT"."faa" AS "faa", "TBL_RIGHT"."lat" AS "lat", "TBL_RIGHT"."lon" AS "lon", "TBL_RIGHT"."alt" AS "alt", "TBL_RIGHT"."tz" AS "tz", "TBL_RIGHT"."dst" AS "dst", "TBL_RIGHT"."tzone" AS "tzone"
  FROM "flights" AS "TBL_LEFT"
  LEFT JOIN "airports" AS "TBL_RIGHT"
  ON ("TBL_LEFT"."origin" = "TBL_RIGHT"."name")
) "wswthdqdlw"
GROUP BY "origin"
